headline.print_headline: Espanyol Appoint Gonzalez to Replace Aguirre as Coach
headline.main: Espanyol Appoint Gonzalez to Replace Aguirre as Coach

lead_paragraph: Espanyol have appointed former player Sergio Gonzalez as coach to replace the departing Javier Aguirre, the La Liga club said on Tuesday.
